{"id": 1291, "genre": 1001, "title": "回顾过去的互联网使用经验，哪些你会觉得不好意思？", "description": "满屏黑历史，举身赴清池。（题图来自：Kirsten Sims）", "record_count": 2961, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161025150025TFNcsQIEveAJa3bh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-26T03:00:39Z", "options": [{"id": 127411, "content": "在QQ空间里写过一堆非主流般伤感的诗和悲春伤秋的日志……", "image": null, "praise_count": 680, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534750}, {"id": 127416, "content": "我竟然转发了那么多无厘头的说说和日志。", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806099}, {"id": 127417, "content": "青春中二 不是互联网的锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 145, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723879}, {"id": 127420, "content": "很多不知所云无病呻吟的空间说说，后来删除的时候真是删到手软", "image": null, "praise_count": 254, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 127437, "content": "路过，回踩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805094}, {"id": 127307, "content": "在微博上写过的无主情话以及伤春悲秋的诗", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 127412, "content": "QQ空间转载日志", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 127413, "content": "为了怕老妈察觉什么就用英文发QQ签名，尽是些矫情的东西……受不鸟了", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805211}, {"id": 127415, "content": "中二的QQ说说和日志", "image": null, "praise_count": 313, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459990}, {"id": 127418, "content": "乡非网名和签名", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488577}, {"id": 127419, "content": "使用QQ空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120503}, {"id": 127438, "content": "留言板的踩，回踩以及所谓的跑堂……当然我说的是别人……哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766691}, {"id": 127446, "content": "写过一些比较矫情的文字，现在看来很幼稚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745418}, {"id": 127449, "content": "密码设置的自己都记不住，还用小纸条写下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165497}, {"id": 127450, "content": "网易照片，qq漂流瓶", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165497}, {"id": 127454, "content": "不停地刷微博，转微博。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651741}, {"id": 127308, "content": "飛翔の眼涙这种中二网名", "image": null, "praise_count": 265, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 127414, "content": "留邮箱好人一生平安???", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670603}, {"id": 127424, "content": "不转不是中国人", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 127425, "content": "每天发心情（那时候还不叫说说），记的和流水账一样?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273282}, {"id": 127431, "content": "对过去的设备感到不可思议，这玩意你居然能忍?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809907}, {"id": 127434, "content": "qq空间肥猪流相册及相片 害羞", "image": "img/option/option/201610261230465GQKIuTq2opm0r7k.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809925}, {"id": 127435, "content": "空间里不堪回首的过去我都留着，为了偶尔看到能提醒自己，后一秒的你看前一秒的你，永远是弱智。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765383}, {"id": 127436, "content": "来看看你。记得回踩哦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762580}, {"id": 127440, "content": "小号偷踩别人的校内", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809331}, {"id": 127441, "content": "第一个网名：阳光男孩?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809953}, {"id": 127442, "content": "太多了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807504}, {"id": 127443, "content": "以前微博上写的那些肉麻没营养话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 127444, "content": "在社交网站上晒一些很蠢的看法…永远要记住人都是要变的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491533}, {"id": 127445, "content": "傻人傻语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808843}, {"id": 127447, "content": "高一的时候用QQ玩网恋??", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809982}, {"id": 127448, "content": "以前愤怒下做的事；所谓的承诺；各种情况所对应的感想及要所改变等。好多种我们以回不到的那些年那些事……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809813}, {"id": 127451, "content": "看到別人發非主流說說??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783139}, {"id": 127453, "content": "心在痛 泪在流这一类似肥猪流个性签名", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553363}, {"id": 127457, "content": "不转不是中国人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718057}, {"id": 127305, "content": "我为啥会给这种糟糕电影打五星", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 127306, "content": "我竟然标记过这么多张嘉佳笛安什么的，好羞耻", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 127422, "content": "门，热，tegn系列，美国禁忌，捂脸走人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699020}, {"id": 127423, "content": "QQ空间招谁惹谁了~", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473880}, {"id": 127426, "content": "和前基友的豆油。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593854}, {"id": 127429, "content": "有种叫博客的东西里面有太多不堪的过去……", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127272}, {"id": 127430, "content": "还留着非主流照片…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 558938}, {"id": 127432, "content": "太污了……不忍直视?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776519}, {"id": 127433, "content": "说句污的，n年前，大概以前深夜泡网吧，总是会被聊了很久的网友摆一道，我看看你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809917}, {"id": 127452, "content": "数赞的个数?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810020}, {"id": 127455, "content": "多次主动搜索2区、八组入口。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769164}, {"id": 127456, "content": "在严格控制好友数量的情况下，却还在乎校内网的浏览人数，以及当时坚决不偷菜的无聊决心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245714}, {"id": 127458, "content": "鄙视QQ 用MSN 加一堆外国网友还以为自己很屌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793331}, {"id": 127488, "content": "那些当时多么在乎，多么激动的人和事情统统发说说写出来，现在删都删不赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804409}, {"id": 130560, "content": "转发此说说，10分钟后会有惊喜??（中毒）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821556}]}